  • Classes in org.vngx.jsch.kex used by org.vngx.jsch.kex 
    Class and Description
    AbstractDHKexAlgorithm
    Abstract implementation of KexAlgorithm for Diffie-Hellman based key exchange algorithms.
    DHGexSha1KexAlgorithm
    Implementation of KexAlgorithm for "diffie-hellman-group-exchange-sha1" key exchange for SSH.
    DHGroupKexAlgorithm
    Base implementation of KexAlgorithm for performing the two standard Diffie Hellman based key exchange as described in RFC 4253.
    DiffieHellman
    Interface to define a Diffie-Hellman (DH) key exchange.
    KexAlgorithm
    Abstract class for defining key exchange algorithm implementations.
    KexException
    Implementation of JSchException for key exchange exceptions.
    KexProposal
    Value object to store the key exchange proposals guessed from the client's and server's proposals during a key exchange.
    KexProposal.Proposal
    Enum constants for the key exchange proposal types.
